snippet.title: Space Trash Scavenger Announcement Trailer - Paradox Arc
snippet.description:
Grab your jetpack and explore procedural asteroid fields, derelict spaceships and abandoned outposts. Build your Space Rig to process scavenged trash. Craft, trade and fight your way to success in this interstellar, open-world survival sandbox.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/spacetrashscav
Discord: https://discord.gg/mpJRBXnCHH
